highlights.text: “That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 18 weeks straight.
“do re mi” by blackbear is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 45 spots at #81.
“There's Nothing Holdin' Me Back” by Shawn Mendes is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “HUMBLE.” is the highest at #3.
